All right.

00:00:33.046 --> 00:00:34.446 A:middle
So, we're really excited

00:00:34.446 --> 00:00:37.616 A:middle
about introducing you
to PhotoKit today.

00:00:37.616 --> 00:00:40.606 A:middle
PhotoKit is comprised
of two frameworks.

00:00:40.606 --> 00:00:42.736 A:middle
The first framework is
the Photos Framework,

00:00:43.046 --> 00:00:46.716 A:middle
which gives you access
to the photos and videos

00:00:46.896 --> 00:00:48.656 A:middle
from the user's photo library.

00:00:49.436 --> 00:00:52.066 A:middle
And you can use it to
build a full-featured app

00:00:52.366 --> 00:00:54.196 A:middle
like the built-in
Photos application.

00:00:54.976 --> 00:00:57.836 A:middle
The second framework is
the Photos UI framework,

00:00:58.186 --> 00:01:00.316 A:middle
and this is a framework
that will allow you


WEBVTT
